text: @FedExHelp I dropped off a package last Sept 20 at one of your FedEx-Safeway locations. Until today, tracking says the package still hasn't been picked up. When will the recipient receive it?

@pikdig Hello Chris, my name is Karin. I apologize for the inconvenience this has caused, I would be happy to look into this matter. Please DM the tracking number, delivery address and contact information. Thank you!
